reviewText: Sid and Marty Krofft Collector's Edition Volume 9: Episodes on this volume include HR Pufnstuf: You Can't Have Your Cake, Bugaloos: The Love Bugaloos, BigFoot and WildBoy: Black Box part 1, Sigmund and the Sea Monsters: The Curfew Shall Ring Tonight, Far Out Space Nuts: Tower of Tagot, BigFoot and WildBoy: Black Box part 2. This is volume 9 of the Columbia House series.
